SUMMARY aggregates every expense in the ledger into per-state counts and dollar totals, producing a short plain-text report suitable for a weekly email body. It takes no parameters. The program is consumed by a Chaprola /schedule cron that runs it every Monday morning and delivers the output to chaprola-expenses@chaprola.org. This is the showcase for scheduled autonomous reporting — no user interaction required, data flows out on a recurring cadence.
